Program: Discovery
Title: The Story of Aids - the discovery of HIV
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryjf
Last Broadcast Date: 23 October 2003
A series of programmes on Aids, how a strange new disease emerged in the 1970s. The first in the series looks at the discovery of HIV, beginning with the early outbreaks of a new illness amongst gay men in America in the 1970s. Scientists raced to identify the cause and then to research the drug therapies to treat it. Presenter: Allan Little. Show less